verbose_text: In contrast, the increase in GABA B IPSCs produced by AM251 was significantly larger in the presence of the MGL inhibitor JZL184 (10 muM; AM251 alone = 115.4% +/- 1.6% of control, n = 6; AM251 + JZL184 = 132.6% +/- 3.9% of control, n = 5; unpaired t test, p < 0.01; XREF_FIG).
